         <abstract>
            <p>The village headmen and community heads of <placeName ref="#solapur">Solapur</placeName> are to be summoned to give testimony about
               the ownership of a row of shops, which is contested by the merchant <persName ref="#adiSethi">Adi Sethi</persName> and the merchant and landlord (desai) <persName ref="#narSethi">Nar Sethi</persName>.</p>
         </abstract>
