   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_sDeshmukh_1582_bism_rumal4_07_r1.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="per" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>ا</p>
         </div>
            <div corresp="#orig_div1" xml:id="trans_div1">
               <p>Alif</p>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="top left margin">
               <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned><gap/></mentioned></stamp></p></div>
            <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2"><p><stamp type="seal">Black starburst ink seal<mentioned><gap/></mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>دستخط
               <lb/>باسم
               <persName ref="#adiSethi">اد سیتهی</persName>
               بن رامسیتهی سیتهیا قصبه
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="#solapur">سدلاپور</placeName>
               <date calendar="#suhur"> سهور سنه ثلاث ثمانین تسعمایه</date>
               <lb/>چنان کتبه برده که دوکان قصبه مذکور
               <lb/>سر ولای راسته میراث خود است
               <lb/>درینوقت
               <persName ref="#narSethi">نرس سیتهی</persName>
               دیسای
               فرمان
               <lb/>اورده است که سر ولای دوکان
               <lb/>بحکم منصفی بدهانند بنابران هر دو
               <lb/>قرار دادیم که مقدمان و پنجاه دو قوم
               <lb/>قصبه مذکور را کل 
               <persName ref="#siddharama">سدرام</persName>
               <gap></gap>
               <lb/>اگر ايشان دوکان سر ولای راسته 
               <persName ref="#narSethi">نرس سیتهی</persName>
               <lb/>دیسای است این نوع گواهی خواهند داد
               <lb/>دوکان بخود نسبت ندارد اگر ازین سخن
               <lb/>تجاوز شود گنهگار دیوان باشم
               <lb/>
               <num>۲۳</num>
               ماه جماد
               <unclear>الاخر</unclear>
               سنه
               <unclear><num>۹۹۲</num></unclear>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p> 
               <lb/>Writing<lb/>
               In the name of <persName ref="#adiSethi">Ad Sethi</persName>, son of Ram Sethi, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sethiya">sethiya</ref> of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba</ref><lb/> 
               of <placeName ref="#solapur">Sandlapur [Solapur]</placeName> in the Suhur year <date calendar="#suhur">three eighty nine-hundred</date> [983].<lb/> 
               Such a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_katba">katba</ref> has been brought that [among] the shops in the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba</ref>,<lb/> 
               possession of a row of shops is my patrimony.<lb/> 
               At this time, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_desai">desai</ref> <persName ref="#narSethi">Nars Sethi</persName> has brought a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_farman">farman</ref> [stating]<lb/> 
               that possession over the shops<lb/> 
               should be given [to him] by order of the judge. On account of this both of us<lb/> 
               struck an agreement that the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muqaddam">muqaddams</ref> and the fifty two communities<lb/> 
               of the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba</ref> [should gather at] the <persName ref="#siddharama">Siddharama</persName> [temple], and<lb/> 
               if they, [seeing that] the shop is in the control of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_desai">desai</ref> <persName ref="#narSethi">Nars Sethi</persName>,<lb/> 
               should provide testimony [to that fact],<lb/> 
               [then], the store has no connection to me. If from this speech<lb/> 
               there should be any deviation, then I will be a criminal of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref>.<lb/> 
               23 in the month of Jumada <unclear>al-Akhir</unclear><note>al-Akhir (the last) is a common variation on al-Sani (the second).</note> year <unclear>992</unclear>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="middle">
            <p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned><gap/></mentioned></stamp>
               <stamp type="seal"><mentioned><gap/></mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Black octagonal ink seal<mentioned><gap/></mentioned></stamp>
               <stamp type="seal">Black circular ink seal<mentioned><gap/></mentioned></stamp><note>These seals appear at the bottom of the first image but in the middle of the physical document.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <pb n="2r" facs="lf_sDeshmukh_1582_bism_rumal4_07_r2.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="mar" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>दर बदीगी अज दीवाणे 
               <lb/>मामले 
               <placeName ref="#solapur">सोनलपूर</placeName> 
               साहेब 
               <lb/>सदर गोसावीयाचे बदी 
               <lb/>गासी 
               <lb rend="empty"/> <lb/>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>द||</abbr>
                  <expan>दस्तखत</expan>
               </choice>
               <choice>
                  <abbr>ब||</abbr>
                  <expan>बेनाव</expan>
               </choice> 
               <persName ref="#adiSethi">आदी सेठी</persName> 
               बीन रमी से- 
               <lb/>ठी सेठीया 
               <choice>
                  <abbr>क||</abbr>
                  <expan>कसबा</expan>
               </choice> 
               मजकूर 
               <choice>
                  <abbr>सु||</abbr>
                  <expan>सुहूर</expan>
               </choice> 
               सन 
               <lb/><date calendar="#suhur">सलास समनीन व तीसमेया</date> 
               करणे 
               <lb/>लीहून दीधले कतबा यैसाजे 
               <choice>
                  <abbr>क||</abbr>
                  <expan>कसबा</expan>
               </choice> 
               <lb/>मजकुरचे रस्ता दुकान सरवीले 
               <lb/>आमचे मीरसी पीडी दर पीडी चली- 
               <lb/>ले आहे दर वक्त 
               <persName ref="#narSethi">नर सेठी</persName> 
               देसाई दी- 
               <lb/>वाणाचे फर्मान आणीले असे जे <gap/>
               <lb/><gap/>पीडी दर पीडी चलिले आहे म्हणौ[न]  
               <lb/>मुनसीफ करऊन देवणे म्हणौन 
               <lb/><gap/>हर दो घेऊन<gap/>नेम केले 
               <lb/>आहे 
               <choice>
                  <abbr>क||</abbr>
                  <expan>कसबा</expan>
               </choice> 
               मजकुरीचे मोकदम व <gap/> 
               <lb/><gap/> कुम लहन थोर मीलून 
               <lb/><persName ref="#siddharama">सिदरम देवचे</persName> 
               प्रसाद घालून 
               <lb/>धर्मत पसुणे 
               <persName ref="#narSethi">नर सेठीचे</persName> 
               दुकन म्ह- 
               <lb/>णौन बोलीले जरी तेचे दुबाले 
               <lb/>करणे तेवरी हरकता केले तरी 
               <lb/>दीवाणाचे गुन्हेगार असे हे कत- 
               <lb/>बा आमची सही छ २३ माहे जमादि- 
               <lb/>लाखर 
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p>
               <lb/>In compliments from the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref> 
               <lb/>of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muamala">muaʿmala</ref> <placeName ref="#solapur">Sonalapur</placeName> to the 
               <lb/>compliments of the exalted 
               <lb/>masters  
               <lb rend="empty"/>
               <lb/>Writing in the name of <persName ref="#adiSethi">Adi Sethi</persName>, son of Rami Sethi, 
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sethiya">sethiya</ref> of the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba</ref> in the Suhur year 
               <lb/>of <date calendar="#suhur">three eighty and nine-hundred</date> [983], the reason [being that] 
               <lb/>a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_katba">katba</ref> is written. Such that 
               <lb/>possession over the aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba’s</ref> row of shops
               <lb/>has been our patrimony from generation to generation. 
               <lb/>At this time, the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_desai">desai</ref> <persName ref="#narSethi">Nar Sethi</persName>  
               <lb/>brought a <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_farman">farman</ref> of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref> such that<gap/>
               <lb/>[the patrimony] has proceeded from generation to generation so 
               <lb/>justice should be effected. So  
               <lb/><gap/><unclear>a procedure has been established</unclear>. 
               <lb/>The aforementioned <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qasba">qasba’s</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_muqaddam">muqaddams</ref> and<gap/> 
               <lb/>communities small and large should be gathered 
               <lb/>and caused to make an offering to <persName ref="#siddharama">Siddarama Dev</persName> 
               <lb/>and ask rightly<gap/>If the shops belong to <persName ref="#narSethi">Nar Sethi</persName>, 
               <lb/>so they say, then custody of it 
               <lb/>should be given [to him]. After this, if any opposition should be made 
               <lb/>then may [they] be criminals of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_diwan">diwan</ref>. This <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_katba">katba</ref> 
               <lb/>is approved by us. On the date 23 of the month of 
               <lb/>Jumadi al-Akhir.
            </p>   
         </div>   
      </body>
   </text>
